"{\"uid\": \"inews.co.uk-inews-lifestyle-the-paris-olympics-taught-us-that-competition-doesnt-need-to-be-cruel-3231796\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"IMPARTIAL NEWS + INTELLIGENT DEBATE Account One thing that filled me with joy was the genuine camaraderie between different competitors at a time when society feels divided TheParis Olympicsbrought us all a lot of joy.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"NEWS\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 14}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 74, \"to\": 77}, {\"ngram\": \"the genuine camaraderie\", \"from\": 82, \"to\": 105}, {\"ngram\": \"different competitors\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 135}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 145}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 158}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympicsbrought\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 197}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 200}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if we are not usually sports fans, one thing shone throughout that event - and that was a sense of community.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports fans\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"one thing\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"that event\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 322}, {\"ngram\": \"community\", \"from\": 326, \"to\": 335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympics brought together a global community - and at a time when the world was feeling divided.\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a global community\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One thing that filled me with joy while watching was the genuine camaraderie between different competitors.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One thing\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"the genuine camaraderie\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"different competitors\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a society that often pushes the idea that in order to be we must put others down, it was refreshing to see the opposite.\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a society\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 612}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposite\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being competitors, theirempathy for others shone through- as did their ability to rise above success and instead be kind, supportive and respectful.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 708}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"their ability\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This translates well into why we need to stop and reflect about what success is, and change the idea of how we want to live, work and be, not just for others but also for our own health and wellbeing.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what success\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"our own health\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"wellbeing\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1040}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The concept of competition and survival of the fittest in evolutionary biology is one that we study when it comes to other ecosystems.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The concept\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"survival\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1082}, {\"ngram\": \"evolutionary biology\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1121}, {\"ngram\": \"other ecosystems\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We talk about animals and plants needing to compete for light or food or resources.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"animals\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"plants\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"light\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"resources\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is either between different species - interspecific - or betweenindividuals of the same species- intraspecific.\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"different species - interspecific\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"betweenindividuals\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"the same species- intraspecific\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1378}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Intraspecific competition is often described as being more intense and having significant impact because the individuals and their role or niches overlap more.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Intraspecific competition\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"significant impact\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"the individuals\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1501}, {\"ngram\": \"their role\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"niches\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Humans have this competitive evolutionary drive and very occasionally, in moments of real crisis, this drive and reaction is absolutely necessary.\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Humans\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"this competitive evolutionary drive\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"moments\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"real crisis\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"this drive\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"reaction\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in most scenarios - like at work, in traffic jams, friendshipgroups or family dynamics- this competition is not necessary.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most scenarios\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic jams\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"friendshipgroups\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"this competition\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, it can actually be to your detriment.\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"your detriment\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An evolutionary drive that was designed to bring you success, happiness and sustainability, actually causes the opposite.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An evolutionary drive\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1929}, {\"ngram\": \"happiness\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"the opposite\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can cause division, unhappiness, lack of support and stress.\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"division\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"unhappiness\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2042}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can actually impact your mental and physical health.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your mental and physical health\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Take the example of a working environment where individuals in a team are pitted against each other.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the example\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"a working environment\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2153}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Up to a point, this can increase and improve output, but there is a tipping point where that then breeds toxicity, relationship dysfunction and even bullying or other behaviours that are not good for mental wellbeing.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"output\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"a tipping point\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"toxicity\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"relationship dysfunction\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"other behaviours\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"mental wellbeing\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can celebrate our competitors and still becompetitive with them in a healthy way.\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our competitors\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"a healthy way\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To do this we need to see beyond the illusions that society draws.\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the illusions\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2563}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike animal and plant systems, in most circumstances where you are either encouraged to be competitive in a toxic way or you choose to be, there are actually enough resources for everyone.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"animal and plant systems\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2616}, {\"ngram\": \"most circumstances\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2639}, {\"ngram\": \"a toxic way\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2704}, {\"ngram\": \"enough resources\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2761}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That might be space to talk in a meeting or time for your to progress in your role.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"a meeting\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"your role\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In your friendship groups,there is likely enough time, space and energy for everyone's life updates and no need to take over the conversation or to put someone else down.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 3031, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your friendship groups\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"likely enough time\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2932}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone's life\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"no need\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2972}, {\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a family unit, instead of parents \\\"favouring\\\" one child and encouraging sibling rivalries, there is enough love and praise to go around.\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a family unit\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3048}, {\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"one child\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"sibling rivalries\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"enough love\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3146}, {\"ngram\": \"praise\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most resources in these scenarios - like love, time, space and recognition- are plentiful.\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most resources\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3186}, {\"ngram\": \"these scenarios\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3217}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3219, \"to\": 3223}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"recognition-\", \"from\": 3235, \"to\": 3247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We think that the only thing that will benefit us is if we succeed in the way we think we should.\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only thing\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3313}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But praising others when they do well improves our sense of teamwork and the quality of our relationships.\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3381}, {\"ngram\": \"our sense\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3418}, {\"ngram\": \"teamwork\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3430}, {\"ngram\": \"the quality\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3446}, {\"ngram\": \"our relationships\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can alsolearn from others in their success- what they did well, how we can improve and take advice from them.\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"their success-\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3516}, {\"ngram\": \"advice\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are also more likely to get praise and validation from others if we have treated them well, and support if we encounter a difficult time later, thus future-proofing our wellbeing.\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"praise\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3620}, {\"ngram\": \"validation\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3635}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"a difficult time\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"our wellbeing\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Giving praise to others, validating them, being kind and celebrating them actually has benefits for our own wellbeing.\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"praise\", \"from\": 3774, \"to\": 3780}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3784, \"to\": 3790}, {\"ngram\": \"benefits\", \"from\": 3854, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"our own wellbeing\", \"from\": 3867, \"to\": 3884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Research has shown that giving compliments increases our own happiness, creates and cultivates gratitude.\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 3991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Research\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 3894}, {\"ngram\": \"compliments\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3928}, {\"ngram\": \"our own happiness\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3956}, {\"ngram\": \"cultivates\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 3980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also has been shown to strengthen our personal relationships which are a mainstay of our physicaland emotional health.\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our personal relationships\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4056}, {\"ngram\": \"a mainstay\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4077}, {\"ngram\": \"our physicaland emotional health\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we experience more positive emotions than negative ones - like jealousy, resentment or anger - we also protect our health and wellbeing, as the predominant type of emotion we feel is a strong predictor of wellbeing.\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more positive emotions\", \"from\": 4134, \"to\": 4156}, {\"ngram\": \"negative ones\", \"from\": 4162, \"to\": 4175}, {\"ngram\": \"like jealousy\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4191}, {\"ngram\": \"resentment\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4203}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4212}, {\"ngram\": \"our health\", \"from\": 4231, \"to\": 4241}, {\"ngram\": \"wellbeing\", \"from\": 4246, \"to\": 4255}, {\"ngram\": \"the predominant type\", \"from\": 4260, \"to\": 4280}, {\"ngram\": \"emotion\", \"from\": 4284, \"to\": 4291}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong predictor\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4372}, {\"ngram\": \"All rights\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 Associated Newspapers Limited.\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4396}]}]}"